Interface Notifyable

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Passable, Wrapper
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AddProductToOrderScreen, AddProductToOrderWindow, AddProductTypeFrame, AddProductTypeScreen, App, Component, EditOrderInFragment, EditProductTypeFragment, FindOrderInFragment, FindProductTypeFragment, Fragment, Frame, ChangeOrderInFrame, ChangeOrderInScreen, ChangeProductTypeFrame, ChangeProductTypeScreen, LoginScreen, MainMenuScreen, MainWindow, NavigatorBarFragment, NavigatorFrame, NewOrderInFrame, NewOrderInScreen, OrderInProductFragment, Screen, SessionBarFragment, Window

    public interface Notifyable
    Rozhrani objektu, kteremu muze byt odeslano oznameni o nejake udalosti. Obvykle jedine rozhrani, kterym komunikuji vestavene graficke komponenty s rodici. Vestavene komponenty pomoci nej obvykle odeslou rodici oznameni, ze u nich doslo ke zmene. Ten si dalsi podrobnosti jiz musi sam nacist z dcerinnych komponent.
